claim.claim-text:
1. A method of making an optical body, the method comprising:
(a) disposing on a substrate a plurality of first particles comprising a first cholesteric liquid crystal composition;
(b) disposing on the substrate a second cholesteric liquid crystal composition to form a structure with the first cholesteric liquid crystal composition; and
(c) converting the first and second cholesteric liquid crystal compositions into first and second cholesteric liquid crystal materials, respectively, wherein the first cholesteric liquid crystal material has a pitch different than the second liquid crystal material;
